title: Mancala Set—Navy Marble
description:
Mancala is one of the oldest two-player strategy games in the world, having been played throughout Africa and Asia for over seven thousand years. Though its origins date back to ancient Egypt, our thoroughly modern version will surely please both novice and seasoned players alike. Each set is constructed by hand of FSC certified solid Ash in Los Angeles CA. Securely clasps for play on the go. Includes 48 playing stones.

  • Dimensions: 10.5 x 6.5 x 3 in when closed, 21 x 6.5 x 1.5 in when open to play
  • Materials: FSC certified Ash wood
